d-strike-blamed-in-south-korean-f-35-belly-landing-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20catastrophic%20mid-flight%20bird%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E%20caused%20an%20F-35%20pilot%20to%20make%20a%20%26quot%3Bbelly%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20gear-up%20landing%2C%20at%20Seosan%20Air%20Base%2C%20near%20the%20country's%20eastern%20coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20South%20Korean%20pilot%20walked%20away%20from%20the%20high-risk%20maneuver%20unharmed%2C%20but%20the%20damage%20left%20the%20Lockheed%20Martin%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20unfit%20for%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreatimes.co.kr%2Fsouthkorea%2Fdefense%2F20230523%2Fhigh-tech-f-35a-may-be-dumped-after-eagle-collision%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year%20after%20the%20bird-strike%20incident%20that%20South%20Korea%20was%20considering%20dumping%20the%20fighter%20after%20estimated%20repair%20costs%20to%20get%20the%20jet%20flying%20again%20following%20its%20unfortunate%20run-in%20with%20an%20eagle%20could%20be%20almost%20the%20price%20of%20a%20new%20F-35.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20F-35%20Joint%20Program%20Office%2C%20a%20new%20plan%20was%20then%20devised%20with%20South%20Korea's%20air%20force%20to%20repurpose%20the%20jet%20as%20a%20training%20platform%20at%20the%20country's%20dedicated%20F-35%20maintenance%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20transporting%20it%20there%20would%20be%20prohibitively%20costly%20and%20difficult%2C%20the%20JPO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20base%20and%20the%20maintenance%20facility%20are%20roughly%2060%20miles%20apart%2C%20making%20it%20a%20tough%20overland%20journey%20for%20the%20aircraft%20and%20its%2035-foot%20wingspan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20JPO%2C%20with%20South%20Korea's%20approval%2C%20opted%20for%20a%20novel%20approach%20to%20this%20problem%2C%20and%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20US%20Navy%2C%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%20personnel%20gathered%20in%20South%20Korea%20to%20work%20with%20the%20