ei-initiatives-memo-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereaction%20to%20the%20DEI%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20one%20of%20several%20%26quot%3Badditional%20headwinds%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20an%20adverse%20impact%20on%20sales%2C%20but%20the%20company%20could%20not%20quantify%20the%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20in%20March%20that%20consumer%20analytics%20firm%20Numerator%20found%20customer%20foot%20traffic%20and%20market%20share%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshoppers-ditching-target-choosing-costco-after-dei-shift-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshifted%20from%20Target%20to%20Costco%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20particularly%20among%20shoppers%20who%20value%20DEI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20respect%20to%20tariffs%2C%20chief%20commercial%20officer%20Rick%20Gomez%20said%20on%20the%20earnings%20call%20that%20%26quot%3Badjusting%20prices%26quot%3B%20was%20one%20of%20several%20steps%20the%20company%20was%20taking%20to%20manage%20new%20import%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComparable%20sales%20fell%20by%203.8%25%2C%20store%20traffic%20was%20down%202.4%25%20and%20average%20transaction%20size%20decreased%201.4%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStore-originated%20sales%20declined%205.7%25%20and%20were%20partially%20offset%20by%204.7%25%20growth%20in%20digital%20sales%2C%20led%20by%20a%2036%25%20surge%20in%20same-day%20delivery%20via%20Target%20Circle%20360.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20many%20levers%20to%20use%20in%20mitigating%20the%20impact%20of%20tariffs%20and%20price%20is%20the%20very%20last%20resort%2C%26quot%3B%20Cornell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20alternatives%20to%20price%20hikes%20include%20sourcing%20more%20products%20from%20the%20US%20rather%20than%20China%2C%20negotiating%20with%20suppliers%2C%20adjusting%20the%20timing%20of%20deliveries%2C%20and%20eliminating%20products%20from%20the%20retail%20assortment%2C%20Gomez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2218c602c2-14e2-4bd0-b6de-e027a71e581f%5C%22%3EBullseye's%20P