west%20of%20Manzanillo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20guests%20arrive%2C%20it%20all%20starts%20with%20a%20dramatic%20entrance.%20I%20still%20had%20a%2015-minute%20drive%20from%20the%20entrance%20gate%20to%20the%20resort.%20I%20navigated%20winding%20roads%20surrounded%20by%20thick%20jungle.%20There%20wasn't%20water%20in%20sight%20as%20I%20passed%20rows%20of%20agave%20and%20spotted%20birds%20singing%20from%20nearby%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20the%20property%20came%20into%20view.%20An%20open-air%20lobby%20featured%20infinity%20pools%20that%20stretched%20out%20to%20a%20rocky%20coastline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%20two%20days%2C%20I%20discovered%20striking%20ocean%20views%20at%20practically%20every%20part%20of%20the%20resort%2C%20from%20the%20golf%20course%20to%20the%20on-site%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20location%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20calendar%20of%20complimentary%20activities%20was%20a%20welcome%20surprise.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20joined%20a%20free%20cooking%20class.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824cee1c6ad288d1480ed65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20joined%20a%20free%20cooking%20class.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20tempting%20to%20jam-pack%20my%20day%20with%20activities%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons.%20I%20eyed%20a%20morning%20snorkeling%20excursion%20and%20debated%20if%20I%20could%20make%20it%20back%20in%20time%20for%20a%20farm%20tour.%20Later%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20I%20planned%20to%20join%20a%20workshop%20on%20fermented%20drinks.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20my%20schedule%20included%20a%20cooking%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20was%20that%20all%20these%20events%20were%20complimentary.%20While%20the%20luxury%20resort%20comes%20with%20luxury%20prices%2C%20it%20was%20refreshing%20to%20know%20that%20I%20could%20fill%20my%20day%20with%20experiences%20that%20wouldn't%20add%20to%20my%20travel%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20common%20theme%20across%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20Four%20Seasons%20properties.%20Four%20Seasons%20Resort%20Hualalai%20offers%20ukulele%20lessons%2C%20lei-making%20classes%2C%20and%20Hawaiian%20quilting.%20At%20Four%20Seasons%20Resort%20and%20Residences%20Napa%20Valley%2C%20guests%20can%20join%20vineyard%20yoga%20sessions%20and%20cocktail-making%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEverything%20is%20on%20the%20property%2C%20so%20you%20never%20have%20to%20leave.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20resort's%20on-site%20restaurants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682638693fe8d3928365fac6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20resort's%20on-site%20restaurants.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlba%20Garcia%2C%20the%20director%20of%20rooms%20at%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20Tamarindo%2C%20and%20Barbara%20Cervantes%2C%20the%20property's%20marketing%20manager%2C%20told%20me%20that%20the%20resort%20is%20designed%20to%20offer%20an%20authentic%20Mexican%20experience%20without%20needing%20to%20leave%20the%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20Mexican%20menus%20created%20by%20award-winning%20chefs%2C%20activities%20diving%20into%20traditional%20drinks%20like%20tepache%2C%20a%20fermented%20drink%20made%20from%20pineapples%2C%20and%20activities%20that%20explore%20the%20surrounding%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'd%20still%20argue%20that%20an%20afternoon%20trip%20to%20the%20seaside%20town%20of%20Barra%20de%20Navidad%20%E2%80%94%2040%20minutes%20away%E2%80%94%20is%20worth%20the%20trek%2C%20the%20Four%20Seasons%20made%20it%20hard%20to%20leave%2C%20offering%20every%20experience%20I%20could%20have%20wanted%20right%20on%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAward-winning%20chefs%20behind%20hotel%20menus%20proved%20to%20be%20some%20of%20the%20best%20bites%20I%20had%20during%20my%20trip.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Food%20from%20Four%20Seasons%20Tamarindo.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681cde62a466d2b74ab567f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFood%20from%20Four%20Seasons%20Tamarindo.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20typically%20opt%20to%20leave%20a%20resort%20and%20head%20into%20town%20for%20local%20foods%2C%20but%20the%20Four%20Seasons'%20menus%20surprised%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20best%20bites%20I%20had%20during%20my%20weeklong%20trip%20were%20at%20the%20property.%20Morning%20pastries%20came%20from%20the%20well-known%20Rosetta%20restaurant%20in%20Mexico%20City%2C%20and%20the%20tacos%20from%20the%20casual%20Nacho%20restaurant%20were%20incredible.%20I%20tried%20foods%20I'd%20never%20seen%2C%20like%20a%20tuna%20chorizo%2C%20and%20stuffed%20myself%20at%20the%20expansive%20breakfast%20buffet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhile%20the%20property%20felt%20ideal%20for%20couples%2C%20it%20also%20had%20families%20in%20mind.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Colorful%20floaties%20sat%20in%20a%20family-friendly%20pool.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6824cf1668a2929008014f8f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EColorful%20floaties%20sat%20in%20a%20family-friendly%20pool.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20place%20with%20striking%20infinity%20pools%2C%20pastel%20sunsets%2C%20and%20private%20rooms%20screams%20romance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20Garcia%20and%20Cervantes%20agreed%20that%20the%20ideal%20vacationer%20for%20Four%20Seasons%20Tamarindo%20is%20likely%20a%20couple%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20thought%20had%20also%20gone%20into%20creating%20an%20experience%20for%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20three%20infinity%20pools%20is%20dedicated%20to%20families%20with%20giant%20pool%20floaties.%20There's%20also%20a%20daily%20arts%20and%20crafts%20session%20and%20an%20exclusive%20event%20for%20teens%20each%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20age%2C%20it%20seemed%20hard%20not%20to%20enjoy%20a%20day%20at%20the%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20welcoming%20staff%20was%20a%20highlight%20as%20well.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Alan%20Reyes%20points%20to%20bees%20at%20the%20resort's%20farm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6826381768a292900801727e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlan%20Reyes%20points%20to%20bees%20during%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20resort's%20farm.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlan%20Reyes%20pulled%20over%20on%20his%20golf%20cart%20to%20show%20me%20a%20calabash%20tree%2C%20which%20grows%20fruit%20used%20for%20maraca%20instruments.%20Twenty%20minutes%20later%2C%20we%20were%20tasting%20honey%20from%20Melipona%20stingless%20bees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20loves%20the%20outdoors%2C%20it%20was%20thrilling%20to%20have%20resort%20staff%20eager%20to%20answer%20my%20pesky%20questions%20about%20the%20plants%20and%20animals%20living%20and%20growing%20on%20the%203%2C000-acre%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20it%20was%20shocking%20to%20watch%20Garcia%20share%20so%20much%20joy%20behind%20her%20job%20as%20rooms%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20rental%20car's%20tire%20was%20flat%2C%20a%20crowd%20of%20workers%20arrived%20with%20an%20air%20compressor%20to%20get%20me%20back%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I