2https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682ca68968a292900801cc93%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22918%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Cyberbeast%20was%20purchased%20in%20September%20for%20about%20%24118%2C000%20plus%20about%20%249%2C800%20in%20taxes.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20trade-in%20estimates%20are%20just%20that%20%E2%80%94%20estimates.%20Tesla%20says%20in%20the%20fine%20print%20under%20the%20estimate%20that%20the%20value%20is%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20current%20market%20conditions%20and%20vehicle%20details%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20estimate%20could%20differ%20from%20the%20final%20offer.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20final%20amount%20Tesla%20is%20willing%20to%20credit%20to%20the%20owner%20could%20end%20up%20being%20less.%20The%20EV%20news%20website%20Electrek%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felectrek.co%2F2025%2F05%2F18%2Ftesla-starts-accepting-cybertruck-trade-ins-confirms-insane-depreciation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tesla%20beginning%20to%20accept%20Cybertruck%20trade-ins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVehicles%20famously%20begin%20to%20depreciate%20as%20soon%20as%20owners%20drive%20them%20off%20the%20lot%2C%20but%20Tesla's%20trade-in%20estimates%20give%20a%20glimpse%20into%20how%20the%20company%20values%20used%20Cybertrucks%20at%20a%20time%20when%20some%20car%20dealers%20have%20shared%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcar-dealer-cybertruck-hard-to-sell-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estruggles%20to%20sell%20used%20models%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trade-in%20estimates%20shared%20with%20BI%20suggest%20the%20Cybertruck%20has%20a%20higher%20depreciation%20rate%20than%20the%20average%20vehicle.%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kbb.com%2Fcar-depreciation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimates%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20new%20cars%20depreciate%20about%2030%25%20on%20average%20over%20the%20first%20two%20years%20and%20lose%20an%20added%208%25%20to%2012%25%20each%20year%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fused-ev-prices-falling-quality-increasing-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEVs%20tend%20to%20depreciate%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20used%20models%20have%20increasingly%20hit%20the%20market%20amid%20the%20EV%20buying%20slowdown%20in%20recent%20years.%20An%20iSeeCars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iseecars.com%2Fcars-that-hold-their-value-study%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20analyzed%20more%20than%20800%2C000%205-year-old%20used%20cars%20sold%20from%20March%202024%20to%20February%202025%20found%20that%20EVs%20lost%20the%20most%20value%2C%20depreciating%2058.8%25%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20found%20that%20trucks%20and%20hybrids%20retained%20the%20most%20value%2C%20with%20trucks%20losing%2040.4%25%20of%20their%20value%20in%20a%20five-year%20period.%20Still%2C%20the%20rates%20that%20Cybertruck%20owners%20shared%20appear%20steeper%20than%20similar%20models%20such%20as%20Rivian's%20all-electric%202023%20R1T%2C%20which%20depreciated%20about%2029%25%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kbb.com%2Frivian%2Fr1t%2F2023%2Fdepreciation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20Tesla%20models%20depreciate%20at%20the%20same%20rate.%20While%20the%20iSeeCars%20study%20found%20that%20the%20Tesla%20Model%20S%20ranked%20among%20the%20top%20depreciating%20vehicles%2C%20with%20an%20average%20five-year%20depreciation%20rate%20of%2065.2%25%2C%20the%20Model%203%20held%20the%20lowest%20five-year%20depreciation%20rate%20among%20EVs%20at%2055.9%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20depreciation%20rates%20can%20vary%20based%20on%20several%20factors%2C%20including%20market%20conditions%20and%20mileage%2C%20the%20Cybertruck's%20decline%20in%20value%20has%20come%20amid%20wider%20pressures%20on%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20political%20backlash%20over%20Tesla%20CEO%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%C2%A0involvement%20in%20the%20White%20House%20DOGE%20office%2C%20Cybertruck%20owners%20have%20faced%20harassment%20and%20vandalism.%20Some%20owners%20have%20expressed%20interest%20in%20selling%20their%20vehicles%2C%20with%20one%20telling%20BI%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20he%20returned%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcybertruck-return-children-safety-bullying-road-rage-concerns-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECybertruck%20soon%20after%20purchasing%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20because%20of%20concerns%20about%20his%20kids%20getting%20bullied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20Musk%20saying%20Tesla%20had%20more%20than%201%20million%20reservations%20prior%20to%20its%20release%2C%20a%20March%20recall%20filing%20disclosed%20that%20Tesla%20delivered%20fewer%20than%2050%2C000%20Cybertrucks.%20BI%20also%20earlier%20reported%20that%20the%20automaker%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-cybertruck-production-drops-sales-slump-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Escaled%20back%20Cybertruck%20production%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20dropping%20targets%20for%20several%20Cybertruck%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Tesla%20employee%3F%20Contact%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20aaltchek%40businessinsider.com%20or%20Signal%20at%20aalt.19.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EUse%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20