20collaborations%2C%20and%20family%20life%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20inspire%20thousands.%20Her%20daily%20content%20reaches%20people%20across%20India%2C%20with%20messages%20on%20fitness%2C%20ageing%2C%20and%20food%2C%20rooted%20in%20her%20upbringing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20eating%20parathas.%20I%20cannot%20suddenly%20switch%20to%20oats.%20So%20I%20tweak%20desi%20food%20and%20make%20it%20healthy.%20That%20is%20why%20people%20love%20my%20recipes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20She%20also%20teaches%20her%20granddaughter%20to%20enjoy%20%E2%80%98me%20time%2C%E2%80%99%20because%20independence%20starts%20young.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20my%20%3Cem%3Enani%3C%2Fem%3E-time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20I%20also%20want%20her%20to%20learn%20to%20play%20by%20herself.%20Kids%20need%20to%20know%20how%20to%20enjoy%20their%20personal%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20advice%20to%20other%20women%20is%2C%20%E2%80%9CDo%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do.%20You%20should%20learn%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20your%20duties%20and%20dreams.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20just%20because%20you%20are%20ageing.%20Self-care%20is%20not%20selfish%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20the%20most%20selfless%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20for%20yourself%20and%20your%20family.%20Your%20loved%20ones%20will%20be%20at%20peace%20when%20you%20are%20healthy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20homemaker%20to%20PhD%20holder%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357087%2Fmotorcycle-biking-trips-from-karnataka-to-kashmir-indian-bikers-tejas-g-r-shares-safety-tips-planning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efitness%20influencer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Roadies%20contestant%2C%20Ashu%20has%20redefined%20what%20it%20means%20to%20age%20with%20purpose%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20joy.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20now%20accepts%20that%20it%20is%20natural%20for%20me%20to%20take%20time%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says