ustralia)%2C%20and%20the%20University%20of%20Toledo%20(USA).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Sharma%20has%20presented%20at%20major%20international%20forums%20such%20as%20the%20Cambridge%20Particle%20Meeting%2C%20IAQM%20(UK)%2C%20World%20Environment%20Expo%202022%2C%20Smart%20Cities%20Conference%20New%20Delhi%202017%20and%20several%20other%20conferences%20across%20Australia%2C%20Brazil%2C%20Egypt%2C%20UK%20and%20the%20U.S.%20His%20expertise%20spans%20air%20quality%2C%20exposure%20science%2C%20urban%20sustainability%2C%20and%20public%20health.%20He%20is%20passionate%20about%20bridging%20science%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20community%20action%20to%20build%20cleaner%2C%20healthier%20cities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20in%20a%20two-part%20series%20exploring%20how%20India%20can%20build%20cleaner%2C%20more%20just%2C%20and%20breathable%20cities%20by%20putting%20people%2C%20not%20policies%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20climate%20action.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhat%20if%20the%20fight%20for%20clean%20air%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20emissions%20and%20enforcement%2C%20but%20about%20strollers%2C%20footpaths%2C%20and%20the%20quiet%20resilience%20of%20everyday%20people%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20global%20research%20labs%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20smog-choked%20streets%20reveals%20a%20truth%20we%20often%20overlook%3A%20real%20change%20begins%20when%20science%20meets%20empathy.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20babies%20breathe%20in%20more%20pollutants%20than%20their%20parents%20and%20the%20urban%20poor%20suffer%20silently%20while%20policies%20stall%2C%20Sharma%20shows%20us%20how%20citizen%20science%2C%20behavioural%20shifts%2C%20and%20grassroots%20innovation%20can%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20cities%20that%20not%20only%20survive%20but%20breathe.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20global%20labs%20to%20local%20streets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20make%20our%20cities%20cleaner%2C%20our%20air%20safer%2C%20and%20our%20communities%20stronger%3F%20After%20spending%20over%20a%20decade%20working%20in%20laboratories%2C%20classrooms%2C%20field%20projects%2C%20and%20ministries%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20answers%20lie%20not%20only%20in%20data%20or%20policy%20but%20also%20in%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20journey%20from%20academic%20labs%20in%20the%20UK%20(University%20of%20Surrey%2C%20Guildford)%2C%20Australia%20(Macquarie%20University%2C%20Sydney)%2C%20South%20Korea%20(Gwangju%20Institute%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology)%2C%20and%20the%20US%20(University%20of%20Toledo%2C%20Ohio)%20to%20the%20bustling%20lanes%20of%20Delhi%20(TRIPP%20IIT%20Delhi)%20and%20Aligarh%20(Aligarh%20Muslim%20University%20Aligarh%2C%20UP)%20has%20taught%20me%20that%20urban%20sustainability%20is%20not%20just%20a%20scientific%20puzzle%20but%20a%20deeply%20human%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2