owfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5fDWMmMHpe8%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22IAQM%20Webinar%3A%20Mitigating%20Air%20Pollution%20Exposure%20to%20the%20Young%20Children%20(MAPE)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20science%20stays%20on%20paper%2C%20people%20pay%20the%20price%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20mountains%20of%20data%20and%20well-meaning%20policies%2C%20the%20gap%20between%20research%20and%20action%20remains%20wide.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20founded%20Sustainability%20Alternatives%20UK%20%E2%80%94%20to%20turn%20insights%20into%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChampioning%20the%20twin%20transition%20for%20SMEs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%2021%20February%202023%2C%20I%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20speaking%20at%20a%20webinar%20hosted%20by%20the%20Institution%20of%20Environmental%20Sciences%20(IES)%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9CSMEs%20Twin%20Transition%3A%20Towards%20Sustainability%20and%20Digital%20Transformation.%E2%80%9D%20As%20the%20Founding%20CEO%20of%20Sustainability%20Alternatives%20Ltd.%20(UK)%20and%20a%20Principal%20Research%20Scientist%20at%20IIT%20Delhi%2C%20I%20took%20this%20opportunity%20to%20spotlight%20the%20critical%20role%20of%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20(SMEs)%20in%20shaping%20resilient%2C%20future-ready%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20talk%2C%20I%20emphasised%20an%20increasingly%20urgent%20truth%3A%20the%20convergence%20of%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20innovation%20is%20no%20longer%20optional%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20existential.%20Especially%20in%20the%20context%20of%20post-pandemic%20recovery%2C%20SMEs%20cannot%20afford%20to%20view%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20transformation%20as%20luxuries.%20These%20are%20the%20pillars%20that%20will%20determine%20their%20survival%20and%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20also%20wanted%20to%20challenge%20a%20prevailing%20misconception%20%E2%80%94%20that%20sustainability%20is%20a%20domain%20exclusive%20to%20large%20multinational%20corporations.%20I%20firmly%20believe%20that%20if%20we%20are%20serious%20about%20inclusive%20progress%2C%20we%20must%20democratise%20both%20sustainability%20and%20digital%20inclusion.%20SMEs%20are%20the%20backbone%20of%20most%20economies.%20Leaving%20them%20behind%20means%20leaving%20behind%20the%20communities%2C%20jobs%2C%20and%20innovations%20that%20they%20drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Empowering%20SMEs%20with%20green%20tech%20and%20digital%20tools%20is%20key%20to%20building%20sustainable%2C%20future-ready%20economies.%20(Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T185317.189_11zon-1747747423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-435369%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20SMEs%20with%20green%20tech%20and%20digital%20tools%20is%20key%20to%20building%20susta