%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20refining%20their%20proof%20of%20concept%20rather%20than%20chasing%20quick%20returns.%20We%E2%80%99re%20more%20interested%20in%20the%20long-term%20impact%20of%20their%20innovation.%20If%20the%20impact%20is%20real%2C%20the%20income%20will%20follow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20supporting%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20issue%20concerning%20the%20lack%20of%20funding%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%20lies%20in%20the%20availability%20of%20robust%20manufacturing%20infrastructures.%20Climate%20tech%20innovation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20only%20about%20breakthroughs%20in%20science.%20It%20also%20depends%20heavily%20on%20process%20innovation%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20scale%20efficiently.%20In%20India%2C%20ventures%2C%20especially%20in%20climate-critical%20sectors%2C%20often%20face%20limitations%20due%20to%20infrastructure%20bottlenecks%20and%20a%20manufacturing%20ecosystem%20that%20is%20still%20evolving.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLogistics%20costs%20are%20in%20another%20area%20which%20has%20room%20for%20optimisation.%20Currently%2C%2013%20to%2014%20percent%20of%20our%20GDP%20goes%20into%20logistics%20compared%20to%20the%20global%20average%20of%208%20to%209%20percent.%20Logistics%20costs%20can%20impact%20the%20competitiveness%20of%20domestic%20manufacturers.%20Factors%20such%20as%20supply%20chain%20inefficiencies%20and%20delays%20in%20transport%20and%20port%20handling%20add%20to%20this%20burden.%20Addressing%20these%20gaps%20presents%20a%20major%20opportunity%20because%20just%20a%201%20percent%20reduction%20in%20logistic%20costs%20could%20translate%20into%20savings%20of%20about%20%245%20billion%20annually%2C%20which%20benefits%20manufacturers%20and%20also%20enhances%20India%E2%80%99s%20global%20competitiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20argues%20Gopalika.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%2